sequenceDiagram
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>Backend
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>(DSP Operator)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant UI as Pipeline UI<br/>(Client)

    rect rgb(200, 230, 255)
        Note over KFP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Metadata Recording
        KFP->>DSP: Pipeline execution triggers
        DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution (artifacts, events, contexts)<br/>gRPC/8080 | Optional TLS | Optional mTLS
        MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE metadata records<br/>DB protocol | Optional TLS | Username/Password
        DB-->>MLMD: Rows affected / IDs
        MLMD-->>DSP: Execution ID, Artifact IDs
        DSP-->>KFP: Metadata recorded
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 200)
        Note over UI,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query
        UI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph(artifact_id)<br/>gRPC/8080 | Optional TLS | Optional mTLS
        MLMD->>DB: SELECT lineage graph traversal<br/>DB protocol | Optional TLS | Username/Password
        DB-->>MLMD: Artifacts, Executions, Events
        MLMD-->>UI: LineageSubgraph response<br/>(Artifacts + Executions + Events + Contexts)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 200)
        Note over KFP,DB: Flow 3: Type Registration
        KFP->>MLMD: PutArtifactType / PutExecutionType<br/>gRPC/8080 | Optional TLS
        MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE type definitions<br/>Schema evolution (add-only properties)
        DB-->>MLMD: Type ID
        MLMD-->>KFP: Type ID (created or existing)
    end
